CustomField.description: This field is optional. It must be manually populated. It is only populated if its associated Risk Grade Factor's "LLC_BI__Type__c" is "Quantitative". This field sets the highest value which is still within the range of the value set for "Risk_Grade__c" on this record. If the risk grade on this record does not have a high limit, this field should be left blank.
CustomField.label: High
